import { Card,Typography,Button,CardActionArea,CardMedia,CardContent,CardActions,Box } from "@mui/material"
import { blog1 } from "./BlogImport"





export const Article=(ImgUrl,date,Title,button)=>{
    return(
        <>
        <Box>


        <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 500,backgroundColor:'red' }}>
      <CardActionArea>
        <CardMedia
          component="img"
          height="300"
          image={blog1}
          
        />
        <CardContent>
          <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5">
              
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2">
            sfaf
          </Typography>
        </CardContent>
      </CardActionArea>
      <CardActions>
        <Button size="small" color="primary">
          Share
        </Button>
      </CardActions>
    </Card>
    </Box>

        </>
    )
}
